Each one teach one! Do you by now know how to dance to
Jerusalema? President Cyril Ramaphosa has urged the nation to take on
the #JerusalemaChallenge on Heritage day, Thursday September 24. The People’s Paper thought hard about those who have two left legs and haven’t
yet mastered the dance. So we’ve put together some tutorials for you to practice so
that when the nation embark on the dance on Thursday, you won’t be left behind. Here are some of the videos. 